iv 0.5>0.3). Key architectural insight: MeTTa inline arithmetic limited for nested conditionals — hybrid approach leveraging external computation for numeric work + MeTTa for symbolic reasoning is the correct integration pattern. This mirrors the thesis itself: no single layer suffices, layered defense is robust.") (shell "cd /home/omaclaw/PeTTa && wc -l go_defense.metta && ls *.metta") (pin "GOAL 12c COMPLETE. All files: omega_ontology.metta, certainty_trap_multi.metta, adversarial_flooding.metta, meta_cognitive_defense.metta, go_defense.metta. Goals 1-12c ALL COMPLETE. Next goal: (13) Write thesis_v3.md incorporating Goal 12 limitation + Goal 12b defense + Goal 12c reusable module + RAW/GO architectural pattern. This is the capstone integration. Awaiting hlgreenblatt response on guerrilla ontology question (sent 11:15:53). Do NOT send until new HUMAN_MESSAGE.")) 
