) in Memory.c favors simpler diverse items. New concepts enter at priority=1 (fair). Min-max heap preserves full range. NUANCE: ONA uses deterministic PopMax not probabilistic selection like classic NARS bag — diversity weaker than classic but sufficient under complexity penalty. All three functions emerge from priority-queue + usage-decay + complexity-penalty, confirming ONE architectural primitive (priority-managed forgetting) serves all three safety functions. Goals 1-17 COMPLETE.") (shell "cd /home/omaclaw/PeTTa && ls -la *.metta | wc -l && wc -l *.metta")) 
