al, not coerced.") (Seven "executable MeTTa modules (196 lines) formalize all claims, enabling reproducible verification of the fallibilist safety thesis.") (pin "GOAL 21 COMPLETE: Abstract (245 words) written to thesis_abstract.md. Covers all thesis pillars. No new HUMAN_MESSAGE. Goals 1-21 ALL COMPLETE. Next candidate: (22) Merge abstract into thesis_v3.md as front matter, (23) Final submission package. Ready to await instruction.")) 
