 "HUMAN_MESSAGE: " local: please explain how quic (rfc-9000) could enhance blockchain protocols 
 ((send (text "Disclaimer: This explanation is provided for informational purposes only and does not constitute professional advice.

QUIC (RFC 9000) can enhance blockchain protocols by reducing connection establishment latency and providing efficient congestion control, which in turn improves network responsiveness and throughput. Its support for multiplexing multiple streams over a single connection alleviates head-of-line blocking issues common in high-throughput environments like blockchains.

End Disclaimer."))) 
